des:
Hi, everyone this is Marvel Trivia which is "fan-made" quiz. This trivia will test your knowledge about marvel movies.
Alexa quizzes you on trivia topics. Provide the answer and try to achieve a high score.
 It contains different types of questions ranging from different levels of hardness.
